<p>If you&rsquo;re writing about an <em>eLife</em> study, please cite <em>eLife</em> as the source of the article and include a link to either the article or elifesciences.org, preferably using our DOI: <a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.7554/elife">http://dx.doi.org/10.7554/elife</a> <span class="st">&ndash;</span> with the article&rsquo;s five-digit extension&nbsp;(e.g. http://dx.doi.org/10.7554/elife.00000). Thank you!</p>

